 ionization degree are estimated to be within 2 \\times 10^-7 and 5 \\times\n10^-6. The four quiescent cores have marginal field-neutral coupling and\nperhaps favor turbulent cooling flows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2011 11:12:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2011 06:40:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
